{"tid":1968351,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（同女友嘈）下個禮拜四係16號定23號","createTime":"2020-04-11T15:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T15:59:27.000Z","uid":49123,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cca4f9f6f2e2787c0469dbf3f4cb823a45411bad","tid":1968351,"uid":49123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:16:08.000Z","msg":"我既定義係星期日至星期一為一個禮拜，所以下個禮拜四係16號<br />\n<br />\n而女友覺得唔會有人咁請，16號應該係今個禮拜<br />\n<br />\n投票前留意發問時間係星期六<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n16<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n23<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2fce28e214c2146f3436e98f21d81d2a0099fe1","tid":1968351,"uid":165482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:19:28.000Z","msg":"16"},{"pid":"1786a279ac4086e1395ceb0f522a40c715e3a9c7","tid":1968351,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:24:58.000Z","msg":"16"},{"pid":"61c25f806d12195dc12ae37232f7d06329b84c28","tid":1968351,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:25:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我既定義係<span style=\"color: red;\">星期日至星期一</span>為一個禮拜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n星期日之後咪星期一, 你一個禮拜得兩日?"},{"pid":"68993018698b163bca5b441f69c76a6c1bc565d9","tid":1968351,"uid":183058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:52:01.000Z","msg":"點會諗到去23？ 咩腦嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3463377e778700523300fd0bd959348b8e247240","tid":1968351,"uid":79081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:55:34.000Z","msg":"感情問題一律建議分手<br />\n<br />\n你女朋友仲要蠢過豬早分早著"},{"pid":"731aefa8686e7404bea30cf6fff2be44f295779a","tid":1968351,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:55:57.000Z","msg":"btw 其實都唔關星期日至六 定 一至日事<br />\n今日問, 咁16號就一定係下個禮拜四啦<br />\n無論係「下個　禮拜四」定係「下個禮拜　四」<br />\n都係16號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話如果聽日／後日問就有可能諗到23<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa064ed7d87980e484065fd6d81537e0cb6ad438","tid":1968351,"uid":18859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"68993018698b163bca5b441f69c76a6c1bc565d9","tid":1968351,"uid":183058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:52:01.000Z","msg":"點會諗到去23？ 咩腦嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:59:27.000Z","msg":"我覺得樓主同女友個諗法係咁<br />\n<br />\n樓主：星期六係今個星期最後一日 所以係下個星期四<br />\n女友：唔理邊日係最後一日 總知嚟緊而未到嘅呢個星期 = 今個星期 所以下個星期係再下個星期四<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但我自己係兩樣加埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}